Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.07,0:00:02.27,italics,7,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:06.51,italics,7,0000,0000,0000,,The depths of their consciousnesses will \Nconnect through Strelizia and merge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.86,sign_196_3__This_is_a_story,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"This is a story of a monster"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:17.62,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,That room was the entirety of my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:23.37,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,A closed world that would never \Ntouch what lay outside the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:27.63,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,That place was the entirety of my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:32.19,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,The Garden, a closed world \Nwhere only children lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.30,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,But that day, I went outside \Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:39.57,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,To this day, I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:42.06,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,To this day, I'd forgotten all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:44.60,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,How vast the sky up above was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:46.56,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,How warm the hand I held was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:50.52,italics,Bo,0000,0000,0000,,And the promise we made.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:52.03,sign_196_3__This_is_a_story,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"This is a story forgotten"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:57.32,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:01:01.59,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, that question \Nnever even crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.57,0:01:06.58,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,I was trapped in that room for \Nas far back as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:12.13,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I had even older memories,\Nbut I soon forgot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.55,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what this was, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:21.85,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Probably a stand-in for \Nwhat you'd call a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:31.81,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,One day, for the first and only time, \Nshe brought me something that wasn't food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:45.22,sign_2483_22_The_Beast_and_th,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Beast and the Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:51.46,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,It was a picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.31,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,As I turned the pages, its bright\Ncolors jumped out at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:56.97,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,as did various shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:02.26,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,It had words, too, but I \Ncouldn't understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:08.75,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,And after that day,\Nshe never showed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:14.78,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this book was \Nmy first "pretty thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.11,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,The outside world surely had many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:23.74,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I innocently \Nbelieved in that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:27.39,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out that I was half-right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.46,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,and half-wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:36.17,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:40.18,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, that question was \Nall I ever had on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.31,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the Garden for as far \Nback as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:50.81,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,We lived there to become parasites who \Nwould fight for Papa and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:54.57,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,All of us children were referred \Nto by our code numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:58.83,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,The lower the number, the higher \Nthe child's potential as parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.95,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,The double-digits up to 099,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:05.95,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,the teens in particular,\Nwere given special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:12.54,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,I was one of them, and I was told \NI was special, unlike everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.10,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.53,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Am I a weirdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.05,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm not like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:34.56,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,They've all stopped smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:38.32,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,They don't get mad or cry anymore, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.45,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,But I still shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.18,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be like everyone else, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.83,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:50.86,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Should I get more injections?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:58.33,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Our codes are in the teens, so we were \Ndifferent from the others to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.22,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:03.55,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Being different is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.57,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want me to give you a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:16.91,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,A name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:21.02,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I gave myself one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:26.57,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,A unique name like the people \Nin books have, and not a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:30.12,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:31.97,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:35.30,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Well? You'll feel better if you're \Nlike me and have a name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:37.27,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:40.05,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.31,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Your name will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.18,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.25,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:49.24,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:53.19,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's how your code \Nis read. 015, for Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:58.08,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.94,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:08.19,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Having a name can make you feel \Nlike it's okay to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.13,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:13.70,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because it's a unique \Nname that exists for you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.71,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,For me alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.92,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.95,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give the others names, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.51,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:29.22,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get everyone in on this, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.91,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.52,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,You can give everyone names!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:36.94,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.15,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,I gave many children names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:43.15,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Samii, Junna, Nakku,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.90,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Toshi, Sakuto, Shinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.66,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,and... Mitsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.27,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,A name is but one way to refer to a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:57.58,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,But just having one made us feel \Nour anxieties fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.71,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.94,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to change your \Ndesignation without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.93,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about giving ourselves names?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.80,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.18,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,One of the teen codes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.22,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't go doing things as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:29.66,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,The adults never answered my questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.53,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,and the other children never asked any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:40.54,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Children were gradually disappearing \Nfrom the Garden at regular intervals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:45.80,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,The adults never told us where they went.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:50.76,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, I was designated \Na special research subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.59,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,and I underwent tests at \Nthe Lab all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.41,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,If I did well, I was given a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:05.82,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, there was still \Nno one who'd answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.22,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.16,flashback,Fra,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:22.46,flashback,Fra,0000,0000,0000,,She's leagues better than \Nall of our past specimens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:26.46,flashback,Fra,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she has \Ndeveloped such a human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:35.68,flashback,Fra,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.18,flashback,Fra,0000,0000,0000,,Look! How amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:41.14,flashback,Fra,0000,0000,0000,,You're an amazing child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.36,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that girl with the horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.09,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Another question?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:57.69,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Return to your room.\NThat's not for you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:04.63,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,That was the first time I'd \Nseen a child with red horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.33,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,And now there was another thing \NI wanted to know more about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.13,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:15.01,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,If nobody would answer me, \NI could just go find out for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.47,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,You there. The lobby isn't that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.52,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it wouldn't be that easy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.57,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any back doors, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:33.05,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew it was so difficult \Nto look for something by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.66,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,That's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.45,sign_12913_120_The_Beast_and_th,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Beast and the Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:16.61,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.50,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:24.16,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, it made \Nme really, really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.70,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.79,flashback,326,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.80,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the Lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.18,flashback,326,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.81,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.53,flashback,326,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get an injection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:45.81,flashback,326,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't, I won't be able to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:52.94,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,All the children there knew what it \Nmeant to get an Elixir Injection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:56.84,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,While you could expect a drastic \Nimprovement in your aptitude scores,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.86,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,it had an incredibly low success rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.22,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,And if it failed, you wouldn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:07.33,flashback,326,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a parasite with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.03,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:13.51,flashback,326,0000,0000,0000,,If I come back alive, will you pilot with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.97,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.22,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.27,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,It's 494 this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.77,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,It was 367 before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.90,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,We just spoke yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.25,flashback,G2,0000,0000,0000,,Papa threw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.54,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.10,flashback,W,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.66,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:48.35,flashback,56,0000,0000,0000,,But Papa and the others made the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.54,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.01,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Code 016.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.22,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.61,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where do the kids go-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:57.43,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.34,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.60,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,His sensitivity is becoming a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:09.27,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,It might affect the other children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:12.19,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we increase his \Nyellow blood cell dose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.43,flashback,Fra,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.19,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:19.65,flashback,Fra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very interested in what kind of parasite \Na child like him will grow up to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.10,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? \NReturn to the Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:04.86,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop doing that. She's in pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.24,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:06.93,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:09.62,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.16,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.96,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,The things I wanted to know \Nkept growing in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.84,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.65,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we give ourselves names?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.30,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the kids who disappear go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.99,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Will Mitsuru come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:28.26,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:32.38,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't the adults give me any answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.65,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't anyone else asking any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:37.82,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:36.03,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand anything, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:40.18,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:49.78,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.45,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I can get you out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.05,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.67,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,You smiled back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.16,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,In this world where questions \Nand answers fell on deaf ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:30.26,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,you shone brightly in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:39.06,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first experience \Nof the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:42.06,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,It was covered in white and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.27,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Everything around me was unfamiliar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.51,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.43,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Don't swallow it! Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.70,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.38,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,You meanie! I was only trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:39.33,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do you not understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:43.33,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Code 016. Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.34,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,What's your code number?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:51.19,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Man, does she not understand me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.06,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:59.22,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,002? I've never seen a \Ncode in the single digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.86,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,002...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:07.41,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Oni? No, Zero Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.36,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Not very good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.21,flashback,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Eo To!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:15.02,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Do you understand what names are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.32,flashback,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Eo To!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.34,flashback,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Eo To!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.71,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I should've thought of a better name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:26.21,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Zero Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.15,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go somewhere far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:38.97,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand his words,\Nbut I knew his voice called to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:41.10,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,I saw things with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.10,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,I walked with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:47.49,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,And it was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.11,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.66,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,It's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.82,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:01.24,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.78,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Aah."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.81,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you sure I can see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:29.65,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:35.49,sign_25167_218_The_Beast_and_th,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Beast and the Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.37,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Beast and the Prince,{\i0} huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:39.12,sign_25307_219_Missing,,0000,0000,0000,,In the deepest, darkest part\Nof a forest lived a tribe,\Nhidden from all. They had \Nlarge wings on their backs\Nand were beautiful, but they were \Nwhat would be called beasts.\N Among them was their princess, \Nwho had huge, ashen wings.\NTheir law said that once one \Nturned sixteen, they would be \Nallowed to fly outside the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:39.12,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, these pictures are so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:44.02,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... "In the deepest,\Ndarkest part of a forest..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.31,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.12,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,They're in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:54.44,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,They should still be nearby. Look for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.47,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.74,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,R-Relax. They'll let us off if I talk to th-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.72,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do about Code 016?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:05.41,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,002 takes priority. If he resists,\Nyou may kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:10.62,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:14.54,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:16.61,sign_26173_231_the_Prince,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2017)}the Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.62,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,"In the deepest, darkest part of a forest
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:24.12,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,lived a strong and beautiful beast princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.62,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Beckoned by the moonlight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:29.37,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,she wandered into a country of humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:34.63,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,and in the moonlit garden of a small castle,\Nshe fell in love with a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.63,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,But the princess was a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:41.01,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,She had ashen wings on her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:44.01,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Not knowing what to do, she went to see
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:46.15,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,a witch who lived at the edge of the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:52.02,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,and said, 'I want to live as a human. \NI want to be united with him.'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:55.02,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,The witch replied like so:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.40,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,'I can help you if you offer me your wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.70,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,But keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:06.24,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you disguise \Nyourself, you are a beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:10.35,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,and you will consume the \Nprince's life one day."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.92,sign_27601_247_Missing_1,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the princess went to see\Na witch who lived in the same forest\Nand said, "I want to live as a human. \NI want to be united with him."\NThe witch replied like so:\N"I can help you if you offer me\Nyour wings. But keep this in mind.\NNo matter how you disguise yourself,\Nyou are a beast, and you will consume\Nthe prince's life one day."\N\N\NThe princess ripped off her wings\Nand was assaulted by pain\Nfar more intense than she had ever felt.\NShe could never fly again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.92,sign_27601_248_Missing_2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, she smiled happily,\Nwith tears of joy\Nstreaming down her face.\N"I'm human! I'm human!\NI'm the same as him now!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:18.30,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I was just thinking \Nhow sad this story is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:23.75,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because one of them isn't \Nhuman that they can't get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.72,flashback,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Awwi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:31.31,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Two people who love each other \Npromise to be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:35.17,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,If they were both human...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.95,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.54,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:46.29,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:47.71,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:51.37,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,It's blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.47,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, I need something to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.35,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Endure it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:05.01,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I read in a book that animals \Nlick their wounds to heal them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:17.98,flashback,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Awwi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.37,flashback,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Awwi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.19,flashback,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Awwi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.51,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Once we get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:29.37,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you forever, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:33.21,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll be your da...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:36.47,flashback,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Da...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:42.88,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but tears \Nflowed from my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.49,flashbacktop,16,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.37,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't because my wound hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.37,flashbacktop,16,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.42,flashback,16,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mistletoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:54.98,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, those were probably tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.94,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,The picture book's world was pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:02.36,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,and I believed that if I was with him, \NI could be the same, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.57,sign_196_3__This_is_a_story,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"But that wouldn't be allowed"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:08.32,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,But this world didn't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:11.35,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:14.33,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not able to find the answers I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:19.34,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,because I'm just a child who doesn't \Nhave the power to protect anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.80,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:26.94,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,That he and I were different creatures, \Nwith blood of different colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.07,sign_196_3__This_is_a_story,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"Erase these memories"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.39,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,and that I was a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.32,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you get for\Nforgetting you're children.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:36.10,flashbacktop,G,0000,0000,0000,,Erase those memories. They're noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:36.10,italics,16,0000,0000,0000,,Zero Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.72,flashbacktop,Sage,0000,0000,0000,,But he's an interesting specimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:38.72,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.72,0:21:40.87,flashback,15,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna give them names anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.49,flashbacktop,326,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:42.69,italics,7,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:43.86,flashback,G,0000,0000,0000,,Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:51.47,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I swore to become human, \Nno matter what I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:56.26,italics,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,If I were the same as him,\NI could be with him forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.13,main,Bo,0000,0000,0000,,Delphinium!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:07.01,main,15,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro, get away from Zero Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.98,italics,15,0000,0000,0000,,She got closer to you to suck you dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:11.01,italics,15,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:13.29,italics,15,0000,0000,0000,,even you'll lose your humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:15.85,main,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:17.38,main,Z2,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:19.09,main,16,0000,0000,0000,,The picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:28.02,main,16,0000,0000,0000,,You were the girl with the picture \Nbook back then, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:35.01,sign_196_3__This_is_a_story,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,"And a story of reunion"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:38.00,sign_33134_360_Episode_1,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 13
